### **ğŸ“ How Consolidated Billing Works**
1ï¸âƒ£ **All member accountsâ€™ costs are combined into one bill.**  
2ï¸âƒ£ **AWS applies volume discounts across accounts.**  
3ï¸âƒ£ **Reports show per-account usage and charges.**  

ğŸ“Œ **Example Use Case:**  
A company with **3 AWS accounts** for **Development, Staging, and Production** can consolidate billing under **one AWS account** to simplify cost management.  

