## **ğŸ”¹ How to Set Up AWS Organizations?**
ğŸ“Œ **Steps to Create an AWS Organization**  
1ï¸âƒ£ Sign in to AWS with the **Management Account**.  
2ï¸âƒ£ Go to **AWS Organizations** in the AWS Management Console.  
3ï¸âƒ£ Click **Create Organization**.  
4ï¸âƒ£ Select **Enable All Features** or **Enable Consolidated Billing Only**.  
5ï¸âƒ£ Create **OUs** (e.g., "Development", "Production").  
6ï¸âƒ£ Invite or create new AWS accounts under the organization.  
7ï¸âƒ£ Apply **SCPs** for governance.  

